<section class="about" id="about">
    <div class="img"></div>
    <div class="texts">
        <h2>About</h2>
        <span class="line"></span>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Minima nobis dolorem quos at accusantium blanditiis omnis doloremque tempore, eligendi officiis quo ipsum quaerat possimus commodi assumenda ipsa enim saepe id?</p>
